snippet.title: Godzilla Creepypasta: Cosmic Chaos
snippet.description:
This is a preview of the new upcoming Cheat Card: Cosmic Chaos.
This card gives the player some new challenges: Black Holes, where the enemy needs to finish the stage as quickly as possible, and Wormholes, which spawns enemies from other planets. There is also the chance that the player will face an entirely new miniboss: The Xilien Mothership.
